suburra is a 2015 italian french neo-noir film directed by stefano sollima , based on the 2013 novel of the same name by carlo bonini and giancarlo de cataldo . the movie was financed by netflix and rai . it stars pierfrancesco favino , elio germano and claudio amendola , and focuses on the connections between organized crime and politics in rome in 2011 . suburra was the name of a suburb of ancient rome .